    backgroundColor: `#07553B`,
    textAlign: `center`
  });
  const DividerColor = styled(Divider)({
    width: `80%`,
    backgroundColor: `#fff`,
    margin: `auto`
  });
  const TitleColor = styled(ListItemText)({
    color: `#fff`,
    textAlign: `center`
  });
  //=================================================================================
  const clickBtn = () => {
    console.log('123')
  }

    <NavBar>

            </ListItemButton>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </nav>
      <DividerColor />
      <nav>
        <List>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemButton onClick={clickBtn}>
              <TitleColor primary="Dashboard"/>
            </ListItemButton>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemButton>
              <TitleColor primary="Calandar" />
            </ListItemButton>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemButton>
              <TitleColor primary="Account Book" />
            </ListItemButton>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemButton>
              <TitleColor primary="Board" />
            </ListItemButton>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </nav>
      <DividerColor />
      <nav>
        <List>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemButton>
              <TitleColor primary="Setting" />
            </ListItemButton>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </nav>
    </NavBar>
  )
}

export default function StyledComponents() {
  return <Nav>StyledComponents</Nav>
}
